data.description: Experience a throwback style revamped with revolutionary Nike Air when you slip into the Men’s Nike Air VaporMax Plus Running Shoes. Mimicking the OG style without losing site of the future of sneakers, these shoes are a must-have for techy sneaker lovers everywhere.
data.features: Compression molded upper for enhanced durability. Bootie construction provides a snug and secure fit. Floating, molded TPU cage is a direct callback to the original 1998 design. Revolutionary VaporMax Air sole for soft, lightweight responsiveness. Durable rubber outsole. Rubber pods on the outsole in high-wear areas for enhanced durability. Integrated lugs provide aggressive traction. The Nike Air VaporMax Plus is imported
